text: Jane Got a Gun is an American action western movie. The movie is about a woman named Jane being married to a bad man. Jane, however, longs for a man named Dan Frost. Natalie Portman plays Jane Hammond. The Weinstein Company will distribute the movie. The movie was released on January 29, 2016. ==References== Category:2016 movies Category:2010s action thriller movies Category:2010s Western (genre) movies Category:American action thriller movies Category:American Western (genre) movies
